snippet.title: Controversy Queens (Episode 4): Human Trafficking and the Heavy State of the World
snippet.description:
In this episode, Angela and Amber go deep into some heavier topics and go through:
✨ An exercise to start to see the truth in your world and start to take control of your reality
✨ Statistics and insight on human trafficking in the states
✨ Why the general population has a difficult time comprehending the severity of this issue
✨ Psychological damage on children when faced with such immense trauma
✨ The culture and history of child abuse
